      <h2 class="lp-section-title">Everything You Need for Digital Payments</h2>
      <p class="lp-section-desc">
        MPay Network provides a complete ecosystem for QR and NFC payments. Explore the features that power seamless transactions.
      </p>

      <div class="lp-features-grid">
        <!-- QR Code Payments -->
        <div class="lp-feature-card" id="lp_feature_qr">
          <div class="lp-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="lp-qr-visual">
              <div class="lp-qr-frame">
                <div class="lp-qr-corner tl"></div>
                <div class="lp-qr-corner tr"></div>
                <div class="lp-qr-corner bl"></div>
                <div class="lp-qr-corner br"></div>
                <div class="lp-qr-scanline"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="">QR Code Payments</h3>
          <p class="">Generate and scan QR codes for instant, contactless transactions. Works offline and supports dynamic payment amounts.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- NFC Tap-to-Pay -->
        <div class="lp-feature-card" id="lp_feature_nfc">
          <div class="lp-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-wifi" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="wifi" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 640 512" data-fa-i2svg=""><path fill="currentColor" d="M54.2 202.9C123.2 136.7 216.8 96 320 96s196.8 40.7 265.8 106.9c12.8 12.2 33 11.8 45.2-.9s11.8-33-.9-45.2C549.7 79.5 440.4 32 320 32S90.3 79.5 9.8 156.7C-2.9 169-3.3 189.2 8.9 202s32.5 13.2 45.2 .9zM320 256c56.8 0 108.6 21.1 148.2 56c13.3 11.7 33.5 10.4 45.2-2.8s10.4-33.5-2.8-45.2C459.8 219.2 393 192 320 192s-139.8 27.2-190.5 72c-13.3 11.7-14.5 31.9-2.8 45.2s31.9 14.5 45.2 2.8c39.5-34.9 91.3-56 148.2-56zm64 160a64 64 0 1 0 -128 0 64 64 0 1 0 128 0z"></path></svg><!-- <i class="fa-solid fa-wifi"></i> Font Awesome fontawesome.com -->
          </div>
          <h3 class="">NFC Tap-to-Pay</h3>
          <p class="">Simply tap your phone to pay or receive payments. Fast, secure, and supported by modern devices.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Merchant Tools -->
        <div class="lp-feature-card" id="lp_feature_merchant">
          <div class="lp-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-chart-line" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="chart-line" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" data-fa-i2svg=""><path fill="currentColor" d="M64 64c0-17.7-14.3-32-32-32S0 46.3 0 64V400c0 44.2 35.8 80 80 80H480c17.7 0 32-14.3 32-32s-14.3-32-32-32H80c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16V64zm406.6 86.6c12.5-12.5 12.5-32.8 0-45.3s-32.8-12.5-45.3 0L320 210.7l-57.4-57.4c-12.5-12.5-32.8-12.5-45.3 0l-112 112c-12.5 12.5-12.5 32.8 0 45.3s32.8 12.5 45.3 0L240 221.3l57.4 57.4c12.5 12.5 32.8 12.5 45.3 0l128-128z"></path></svg><!-- <i class="fa-solid fa-chart-line"></i> Font Awesome fontawesome.com -->
          </div>
          <h3>Merchant Tools</h3>
          <p>Comprehensive dashboard with analytics, transaction management, and business insights to grow your business.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Consumer Wallet -->
        <div class="lp-feature-card" id="lp_feature_consumer">
          <div class="lp-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-credit-card" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="credit-card" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 576 512" data-fa-i2svg=""><path fill="currentColor" d="M64 32C28.7 32 0 60.7 0 96v32H576V96c0-35.3-28.7-64-64-64H64zM576 224H0V416c0 35.3 28.7 64 64 64H512c35.3 0 64-28.7 64-64V224zM112 352h64c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16s-7.2 16-16 16H112c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16s7.2-16 16-16zm112 16c0-8.8 7.2-16 16-16H368c8.8 0 16 7.2 16 16s-7.2 16-16 16H240c-8.8 0-16-7.2-16-16z"></path></svg><!-- <i class="fa-solid fa-credit-card"></i> Font Awesome fontawesome.com -->
          </div>
          <h3 class="">Consumer Wallet</h3>
          <p class="">Easy-to-use digital wallet for everyday payments, P2P transfers, and balance management. Pay anywhere, anytime.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Secure & Reliable -->
        <div class="lp-feature-card" id="lp_feature_security">
          <div class="lp-feature-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg class="svg-inline--fa fa-shield-halved" aria-hidden="true" focusable="false" data-prefix="fas" data-icon="shield-halved" role="img" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512" data-fa-i2svg=""><path fill="currentColor" d="M256 0c4.6 0 9.2 1 13.4 2.9L457.7 82.8c22 9.3 38.4 31 38.3 57.2c-.5 99.2-41.3 280.7-213.6 363.2c-16.7 8-36.1 8-52.8 0C57.3 420.7 16.5 239.2 16 140c-.1-26.2 16.3-47.9 38.3-57.2L242.7 2.9C246.8 1 251.4 0 256 0zm0 66.8V444.8C394 378 431.1 230.1 432 141.4L256 66.8l0 0z"></path></svg><!-- <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved"></i> Font Awesome fontawesome.com -->
          </div>
          <h3 class="">Secure &amp; Reliable</h3>
